        "faq_item_3zg9na": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "med-2",
            "question": "What makes this menopause formula different from others?",
            "answer": "<p>Unlike typical menopause supplements, this formula combines Berkeley Life’s clinically proven Nitric Oxide Support supplement which provides dietary nitrates – the essential building boxes of nitric oxide with purified pollen complex extract. Together, this dual action supplement supports both menopause symptoms and heart health—something no other product on the market does.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_xn9akF": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "med-2",
            "question": "How does Nitric Oxide support women during menopause?",
            "answer": "<p>As estrogen levels decline as your naturally age, your body’s natural Nitric Oxide production also drops which may affect circulation and energy. Supporting  healthy Nitric Oxide production helps promotes optimal blood flow and vitality.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_yibBh7": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "med-2",
            "question": "Is this product hormone-free?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. This formula is 100%  hormone free. It can also be used alongside HRT under supervision of your healthcare provider.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_PpyqdR": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "med-2",
            "question": "How does it support heart health?",
            "answer": "<p>Estrogen levels naturally decline with age which can affect circulation and cardiovascular function. The Nitric Oxide Support capsules support blood vessel relaxation, healthy circulation and cardiovascular function for overall well-being during menopause and beyond </p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_brpzHQ": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "med-2",
            "question": "How do I take it?",
            "answer": "<p>Take two capsules daily—one Nitrate Complex capsule and one Pollen Complex capsule—with water after food. Consistency is key for optimal results and sustained Nitric Oxide support.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_W4qiXp": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "med-2",
            "question": "Can I take this with other supplements or medications?",
            "answer": "<p>As with any new supplement, it’s best to discuss it with your healthcare provider.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        }
